    "body": "I'm confused about how `FrozenUnderFog` can work at all for actors without a footprint.  Its entire job is based around changing the actors state depending on whether its footprint is revealed or not!\r\n\r\nI suspect it may be better (less edgecases, more perf) to create a new `IDefaultVisibility` trait for oil patches if you still need it."
